The paper discusses a method for preserving privacy while conducting statistical tests on sensitive data. This falls under the category of privacy-preserving data analysis, which is commonly studied in the sub-categories of cryptography (cs.CR), databases (cs.DB), machine learning (cs.LG), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and information theory (cs.IT).
